{"tid":1964440,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[腳痛撚] 腳內則同腳爭好痛，行路都要gui下gui下咁行","createTime":"2020-04-08T21:52:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-11T09:18:14.000Z","uid":157310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"a32a7ef331a5fcc811ecf3fee7d2ca9c04a72ca5","tid":1964440,"uid":157310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T21:52:41.000Z","msg":"早排有段時間操返跑步，日日跑5-7k<br />\n跑左4.5日到發覺好似跑傷左，情況就係腳內則痛<br />\n之後就到宜家都無跑<br />\n咁返工就開始黎料，企耐小小就會有腳內則同腳爭痛既情況出現，收工巴士都追唔到，要慢慢行出去<br />\n宜家起身係屋企行幾步都feel到痛<br />\n有無巴打知咩事？係本身有腳底筋膜炎定跑步跑到發炎？<br />\n同如果睇醫生去睇西醫好定中醫？<br />\n感激<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16a0c4b75fbaf2c42f66bb33d7df6fd9da750ada","tid":1964440,"uid":3167,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T21:56:15.000Z","msg":"一係發炎一係生骨刺囉<br />\n唔清楚就去照下"},{"pid":"7c84aac6ea30e09c48be271c6e976eb5d370db14","tid":1964440,"uid":157310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"16a0c4b75fbaf2c42f66bb33d7df6fd9da750ada","tid":1964440,"uid":3167,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T21:56:15.000Z","msg":"一係發炎一係生骨刺囉<br />\n唔清楚就去照下"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T21:58:43.000Z","msg":"想知應該睇中醫好定西醫好<br />\n因為好奇怪，我自己禁落個位又唔會話有痛既感覺<br />\n只係一行，一企先會痛"},{"pid":"7a085b62b4aadc32e2fb9f7b22a114d20165585e","tid":1964440,"uid":34877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T22:02:10.000Z","msg":"扁平足？"},{"pid":"b17f8aaffec2d730ffd2fdb9340e206f04962a69","tid":1964440,"uid":3167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c84aac6ea30e09c48be271c6e976eb5d370db14","tid":1964440,"uid":157310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"16a0c4b75fbaf2c42f66bb33d7df6fd9da750ada","tid":1964440,"uid":3167,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T21:56:15.000Z","msg":"一係發炎一係生骨刺囉<br />\n唔清楚就去照下"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T21:58:43.000Z","msg":"想知應該睇中醫好定西醫好<br />\n因為好奇怪，我自己禁落個位又唔會話有痛既感覺<br />\n只係一行，一企先會痛"},"cite